@NODE "MultiRequest" "MultiRequest"

    pp_MultiRequest n1$ n2$ n3$

    Opens a requester in the centre of the screen
    This requester may contain one or more buttons and will return
    the number of the selected button

    n1$: requester title
    n2$: body text
    n3$: button(s) separated by "|"

    The rightmost button will always return the value 0 (it is
    normally used for 'Cancel'). The numbering of the other buttons is
    as usual (1,2,...) from left to right.

@ENDNODE
@NODE "LongRequest" "LongRequest"

    pp_LongRequest n1$ n2$

    Opens a requester in the centre of the screen
    This requester will wait until a number has been entered
    
    n1$: requester title
    n2$: body text

@ENDNODE
